<p class="ql-align-justify">金莎还回复了“哈哈哈”。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201216/d8a9b57ccfbe41739798e6eff755c49a.png" max-width="600" /></p>
